These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, chess
1. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Game           | scrabble | monopoly |
| Hobby   | chess     | filmmaking  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, daffodil
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, amber
1. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbegonia##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Flower         | daffodil   | begonia      |
| Color   | pink | amber |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, coffee
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, ritmeester
1. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the blend-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Beverage   | coffee | water    |
| Cigar     | blend | ritmeester |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
